notes:
### v1.12.1
#### NEW FEATURES
- shield tracking should be working again
- added the ability to differentiate bard brands (e.g. sound shock, harp of rhythm, stigma)

![brands](https://i.imgur.com/NQFBHlo.png)

#### BUG FIXES AND IMPROVEMENTS
- fixed app crashing when trying to view log with missing data
- added backwards compatibility to view old skill charts on older logs

**NOTE**: due to missing packets, meter must be opened in character select, or before swapping characters, to get correct info.

### Current Functionality
#### Working
- damage meter
- basic logs
- party/self buff uptime tracking (mostly)
- identity (maybe)
- shields (maybe)
- maybe some other stuff
#### Not Working
- rdps
- stagger
- pretty much anything else not listed here

full patch notes on [github](https://github.com/snoww/loa-logs/releases/latest)

send bug reports/suggestions to [ramen shop server](https://discord.gg/RXvTMV2YHu)
